citations:
    citation-adwd-tyrion-iii:
        source: source-adwd
        properties:
            locator: "Tyrion III"
            accessed: "2026-03-06"
        notes: "POV: Tyrion Lannister. Tyrion is now aboard the Shy Maid on the Rhoyne with Griff (Jon Connington), Young Griff, Haldon Halfmaester, Septa Lemore, Rolly Duckfield (Duck), and the boat crew Yandry and Ysilla. He plays cyvasse with Young Griff and begins to suspect the boy's true identity. Tyrion learns that Griff is a disgraced lord in exile. He identifies Griff's accent as being from the Stormlands. The chapter establishes the Shy Maid's company and the tensions within it."
